The German tax payer explained these deliveries in his VAT return and in the ZM.
His right to tax exemption has been recognised.
On the basis of the notification by the Federal Republic of Germany, the German FA will send to the Czech Republic the documents necessary for the subsequent taxation of the purchased goods.
